<title>World Sim Game Documentation Change Summary Ver0.2.6</title>
<style>
body { font-family: Calibri, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt; line-height: 1.35; color: #1f1f1f; }
h1 { font-size: 21pt; margin-top: 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #999; padding-bottom: 6pt; }
h2 { font-size: 15pt; margin-top: 16pt; color: #24364a; }
p { margin: 6pt 0; }
li { margin: 2pt 0; }
code { font-family: Consolas, monospace; background: #f2f2f2; }
</style>
